Class ObjectImages

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.bme.mit.battle_city.gui.ObjectImages

  • public class ObjectImages
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that contains the images of the objects to be drawn. Size of the board: 15x15 map of 40x40 pixel sized objects => 600x600 game field
